Lucy Punch https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lucy_Punch 0 Lucy Punch (born 30 December 1977) is an English actress. She has appeared in films such as Ella Enchanted, Hot Fuzz, Bad Teacher, You Will Meet a Tall Dark Stranger, Dinner for Schmucks, and Into the Woods. She is also known for her role as Esmé Squalor in A Series of Unfortunate Events. Lucy_Punch ( born_30_December_1977 ) is an_English_actress .
